string.text: Dziakujučy zołatu i srebru, jakija zdabyvajecca va ŭzhorkach i skałach, žychary hetaha kraju zjaŭlajucca samymi bahatymi na Zachadasie.
Ludzi Poŭnačy - ciahavitaja paroda. Naščadki Pieršych Ludziej, jakimi kiravali Karali Poŭnačy da zavajovy Aehona.
Dotrakijcy - vajaŭničy kačavy narod, što pierasoŭvajecca vialikimi ordami pa łuhach Uschodasa. Ordy zvyčajna zavucca chałasarami.
Žaleznanarodžanyja nasialajuć Žaleznyja Vyspy i pakłaniajucca Patanułamu Bohu. Dla ich rabavańnie zachodnich bierahoŭ Zachadasa - ład žyćcia.

Darnijcy ŭ bolšaści svajoj zjaŭlajucca naščadkami naroda, jaki ŭźnik kala Raki Rojn na Uschodasie. Pryncesa Nimieryja źbiehła sa svajoj radzimy, ratujučysia ad Valiryjcaŭ, i pasialiłasia ŭ Dornie z vialikaj kolkaściu haściej. Toje tłumačyć, čamu bolšaść Darnijcaŭ vyhladajuć inačaj za zvyčajnych Zachadasaŭ.
Najbahaciejšy z Volnych Haradoŭ. Tut znachodzicca Žalezny Bank i Dom Čornaha i Biełaha.
Naščadki Pieršych Ludziej, jakija patrapili ŭ pastku na poŭnačy ad ściany 8000 hadoŭ tamu. Narody, što žyvuć na poŭdnie ad ściany, časta zavuć ich adzičełymi.

Vajskovy orden, jakomu daručana baranić karaleŭstvy ludziej ad usiakaj pahrozy z poŭnačy ad ściany. U ich šerahach časta sustrakajucca badziahi i złačyncy, jakija sprabujuć paźbiehnuć lutaha hnievu pravasudździa.
Damy, jakija paklalisia ŭ viernaści łordam svajho kraju, ale nasamreč addanyja tolki sabie.
Pieršyja Andały, jakija prybyli ŭ Zachadas, pasialilisia ŭ miascovaści, viadomaj siońnia jak Dalina. Heta surovy łandšaft, atočany Harami Miesiaca.

Žychary hetaha kraju žyvuć na skryžavańni šlachoŭ niekalkich inšych mahutnych karaleŭstvaŭ. U časy zavajovy Tarharyjenaŭ račnyja ziemli znachodzilisia pad uładaj Žaleznanarodžanych. Paŭstańnie pad pravadyrstvam Doma Talli dapamahło Aehonu zavajavać hety kraj. U vyniku, u hetym krai byli atrymany vielizarnyja vaładarstvy.
Žychary vyspaŭ i žychary kala Zatoki Čornaja Vada paśla paŭstańnia Robierta pierajšli pad kantrol Stańnisa Barateona.

Žychary hetych ziemlaŭ nazvany tak z-za častych dzikich štormaŭ, jakija abrušvajucca na ichniaje ŭschodniaje ŭźbiarežža z boku Vuzkaha Mora. Da zavajovy Aehonam hety kraj składaŭ ułasnaje suvierennaje karaleŭstva, jakoje mieła nazvu Štarmavoje Karaleŭstva.
Tutejšyja žychary zjaŭlajucca vychadcami druhoha haspadarstva pa vieličyni z Siami Karaleŭstvaŭ, paśla Paŭnočnaha. Hety kraj maje samyja ŭradlivyja ziemli ŭva ŭsim Zachadasie.

Hetyja ludzi - naščadki staroj Staroj Impieryi His, jakaja była źniščana Valiryjcami padčas Hiskarskich Vojnaŭ. U haradach Zatoki Zaniavolnikaŭ dahetul praktykujecca šmat starych Hiskarskich zvyčajaŭ.
Žychary sprečnych ziemlaŭ pamiž Račnymi i Štarmavymi Ziemlami, jakija z časoŭ Aehona Zavajoŭnika kirujucca niepasredna karalom z Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
Volny horad Norvas - sapraŭdnaja teakratyja, jakoj kirujuć Baradatyja Śviatary. Štodzionnaje žyćcio ludziej stroha padnačalvajecca trom zvanam.
Naščadki tych, chto pakinuŭ Valiryju da źniščeńnia hetaha horada kataklizmam.
Žychary pieršaha Volnaha Horada Uschodasa, jakoj zasnavali Valiryjcy.
Žychary adnaho z Volnych Haradoŭ Uschodasa. Viadomaha jak Horad Viedźmaroŭ.
Žychary samaha paŭnočnaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na vyśpie ŭ Dryhučym Mory.
Žychary samaha zachodniaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na bierazie Zatoki Pentos.
Žychary samaha raźvitaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na bierazie Mora Mirt.
Ludzi z Volnaha Horada, źmiescavanaha na Stupienistych Kamianiach.
Žychary Volnaha Horada, źmiescavanaha na vyśpie ŭ Letnim Mory.
Kłany sa Zrezanych Vyspaŭ z Zatocy Ciuleniaŭ. Z-za adsutnaści kantaktaŭ jany ličać, što kirujuć saboj sami.
Žychary Załatoj Impieryi I Ci, što mieścicca daloka na ŭschodzie.
Žychary Letnich Vyspaŭ z dalokaha poŭdnia, ŭ Letnim Mory.
Ja - zakonny Karol Zachadasa, i ja viarnu sabie tron, jaki pabudavali maje prodki.
Syn uzurpatara padzie pieršym, potym jaho braty.
Voŭk i hadziuka taksama buduć utajmavany, a ja budu rabić toje, što mušu - haspadaryć.
Nikoli nia budzie miru, pakul ja nie adpomšču za svajho baćku!
Vojski Tajŭjina paduć adno za adnym.
Ja nasadžu hałavu Džoffry na piku i pierabju ŭsich Łańnistaraŭ, što trapiacca mnie na vočy adsiul i da Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
Ja - najbahaty čałaviek u Zachadasie, moj unuk siadzić na Žaleznym Tronie. Usie palityčnyja hulni kruciacca vakoł doma Łańnistaraŭ.
Małady voŭk advažny, treba addać jamu naležnaje.
Ale jon trapiŭ u čužuju krainu, a paŭnočniki tut doŭha nie žyvuć.
Ale dom Rojsaŭ zaŭždy isnavaŭ. U nas ciače kroŭ pieršych ludziej, i my byli tut jašče da zjaŭleńnia Andalskich damoŭ.
U minułym my byli Bronzavymi Karalami hor i kiravali ŭsioj Dalinaj.
Dom Tajrełaŭ - adzin z małalikich damoŭ, zdolnych supierničać z Łańnistarami ŭ bahaćci i prestyžy.
My kantralujem Mander, bolšuju častku ahrarnych ziamiel i zdolny sabrać fłot, jaki moža supierničać z Fłotam Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
Ale aproč usiaho, my viernyja sapraŭdnamu i zakonnamu karalu siami karaleŭstvaŭ.
My žaleznanarodžanyja. Nie pryhonnyja, nie raby.
My nie arem ziamlu i nie pracujem u šachcie.
My biarom toje, što naležyć nam.
Dom Nimieros Marteł hanarlivy haspadar Dorna.
My abjadnali našy dom z Karalevaj Nimieryi z Rojnara, tamu my viadziom spravy inačaj, čym u Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
Pakul my budziem ciešycca śvietam i roskvitam tut, naša izalacyja zrobić nas mocnymi.
Ja zabju ludziej u žaleznych harniturach i zrujnuju ich kamiennyja chaty!
Ja zhvałtuju ich žančyn, zaniavolu ich dziaciej i zabiaru ich złamanych bahoŭ u Vaez Dotrak!
Ja daju zarok, klanusia pierad Maci Hor, pakul zorki hladziać uniz u jakaści śviedkaŭ!
Račnyja Ziemli nie pakinuć biez uvahi złodziejaŭ z Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
My hatovyja dałučycca da majho plamieńnika, kali pryjdzie čas.
My - vaładary Pierapravy. Našaj uładzie niama roŭnych u Račnych Ziemlach.
My - vaładary Pierapravy. Našaj uładzie niama roŭnych u Račnych Ziemlach.
Ja - vaładar Pierapravy. Moža, Talli i vaładar Tryzuba, ale nichto nie piarojdzie hetaha mosta i nie abminie majoj bramy, nie addaŭšy mnie daniny pašany.
My - vaładary Pierapravy. Našaj uładzie niama roŭnych u Račnych Ziemlach.
Być dačkoj Nahladnika Poŭdnia, toje maje pieravahi, ale być karalevaj...
Usie nienavidziać Stańnisa. Ja - karol, jakoha varty narod, i maje vojski zrobiać svaju spravu.
Ja addany Karalu Renli da apošniaha ŭzdycha.
Ja zakonny karol siami karaleŭstvaŭ. Kali moj brat-puchlak nie sydzie z pasady, ja i jaho razdušu.
Ja haspadar Vałancisa i samy ŭpłyvovy Tryjarch u Rojnie. Karali zachadu i ŭschodu viedajuć majo imia.
U majoj siamji kažuć: hoły čałaviek maje sakrety; abiasskurany - nivodnaha.
Kali ty dumaješ, što hetaja historyja maje ščaślivy kaniec, ty nie {?PLAYER.GENDER}źviartała{?}źviartaŭ{\?} na jaje ŭvahi.
Ja kachaju cybulnaha rycara, možaš dastać jaho dla mianie?
My - vaładary Pierapravy. Našaj uładzie niama roŭnych u Račnych Ziemlach.
Zabudź pra liniju spadkajemstva, Renli - karol, jakoha zasłuhoŭvaje narod.
Ja vieru ŭ Karalevu Danaerys, jana ŭžo zrabiła ŭsio, što źbirałasia.
Dom Korbrej paklaŭsia Nahladnicy Uschoda, Lisie Arryn, pakul Robin nie pastaleje.
Dom Korbrej paklaŭsia na viernaść Nahladnicy Uschoda, Lisie Arryn, pakul Robin nie pastaleje.
Mianie časta ciešyć dumka, što navat u samyja zmročnyja dni vajny ŭ bolšaści miescaŭ u śviecie absalutna ničoha nie adbyvajecca.
Dom Chanter prysiahnuŭ Nahladnicy Uschoda, Lisie Arryn, da paŭnalećcia Robina.
My budziem stajać na baku Doma Talli da samaha horkaha kanca, kali zapatrabujecca.
Dom Chanter prysiahnuŭ Nahladnicy Uschoda, Lisie Arryn, da paŭnalećcia Robina.
Im the Lord of Driftmark and a king of the seas, like my ancestors before me.
Im sworn to the Lord of the Mander, Mace Tyrell. Where he goes, Ill follow.
Im sworn to the Lord of the Mander, Mace Tyrell. Where he goes, Ill follow.
Im the Sealord of Braavos, I will protect this city and its citizens as I am charged to do.
Some say my uncle is the greatest swordsman in the seven kingdoms, but I heard he fleed to serve a foriegn queen.
Im the King of Lorath, this region bows to me.
We will uphold our vows to House Tully and fight until our last breath if need be. By the way, steer clear of the Brackens, they are bad news.
We will uphold our vows to House Tully and fight until our last breath if need be.
We are sworn to the Lord Paramount of the Trident, but we awefully close to crown here.
We are sworn to the Lord Paramount of the Trident, but we awefully close to crown here.
Stannis is a good man, hes saved my life more times than I can count.

Ive been all over the world, my boy, and everywhere I go people tell me about the true gods, they all think the found the right one. The one true god is whats between a womans legs. And better yet a queens legs.
We bow to no man north of the wall, the freefolk made me their leader because the trusted me.
Were the King of Salt and Rock goes, we follow.
Im the Lord Captain of the Iron Fleet, nothing in the seas can rival our might.
My only goal is to not die so far from the sea.
Were the King of Salt and Rock goes, we follow.
I am the storm, my lord. The first storm and the last.
I would say you know nothing, from how pretty you dress and your pretty hair. You need a touch of the true north in your life.
We serve the king in the north, as long as I deem his judgement worthy.
Walkings good, fightings better, fuckings best!
Were the King of Salt and Rock goes, we follow.
Have you ever heard of the Sword of the Morning? He was my uncle and one of the greatest warriors ever.
Ive been kingsguard and queensguard, but still now I could slice through your lot like carving a cake, if need be.
Dont underestimate the power of the Sand Snakes, it wont end well for you.
Im the ruler of Myr, the craftmanship of my subjects is unmatched, and we put it to good use.
Im the ruler of Pentos, many a king and queen have passed through these gates.
Dont underestimate the power of the Sand Snakes, it wont end well for you.
Im on my way to Kings Landing. The Lannisters arent their debts.
Dont underestimate the power of the Sand Snakes, it wont end well for you.
We serve at the pleasure of the Prince of Dorne.
We swore oaths to the Prince of Dorne, but in times past, oaths were sworn to us in this area.
Im the ruler of Lys, a paradise in the Summer Sea. Even the Valyrians saw her beauty.
We serve at the pleasure of the Prince of Dorne.
Im the ruler of Tyrosh, we have honed our skills in both the land and sea in the disputed lands and stepstones.
The only way to keep the people loyal is to make certain they fear you more than they do the enemy.
I lead the vanguard for the Warden of the South, Mace Tyrell.
Nothing can touch me or my son a top the Eyrie, and my loyal knights of the vale in the field would see that it never came to an ill-advised siege.
I dont see why the crown and the sept cant work together to make Kings Landing a better place.
I serve at the pleasure of Lady Lysa Arryn.
This Kings Landing air doesnt suit me, perhaps somewhere warmer.
I lead the vanguard along side my father for the Warden of the South, Mace Tyrell.
Do you want to fly, I can make that happen.
House Lannister has the gold and the leadership to out class all others, if I do say so myself.
I can call up a fleet to rival that of the royal in a moments notice to serve the Warden of the South, Mace Tyrell.

A man who sees nothing has no use for his eyes, cut them out and give them to your next outrider. Tell him you hope that four eyes might see better than too ... and if not, the man after him will have six.
A Stark must always be at Winterfell, although something is calling me north as far north as north can go.
Ill see to it that winter comes for House Frey.
Im not a lady. Never have been. Thats not me.
Im the Lord Commander of the Nights Watch, we are the shield that guards the realms of men.
Id wipe that smug look off your face in ten minutes in the training yard of Castle Black.
I cant believe I was so smitten by King Joffrey. Im a slow learner, its true. But I learn.
When the snows fall and the white winds blow, the lone wolf dies, but the pack survives.
I swore vows to the King of the North, Robb Stark.
House Stark will survive this treachery, Ill see to it.
Im a bastard, serving in the honorable Nights Watch like my uncle and many before me. Yet I do feel theres more to my story somehow.
I know no king but the king in the north whose name is Stark.
I know no king but the king in the north whose name is Stark.
Politics? Thats why I have my small council, so they can handle the tedious and mundane.
Get out of my face with that political hogwash, the only thing that matters is what the king says.
Danaerys is my queen, I will give my life for hers without batting a eye.
Could care less about it, but if you ever see these eyes pale blue, put a couple fire arrows through them.
He serve at the pleasure of the King in the North.
Where the King of the North goes, my axe follows.
Long live the King in the North!
We follow the King in the North, for now.
The gods forbid the others take my children, nothing more terrifying to me.
I will ride with the riverlords into battle, no matter the price.
We ride with House Tully for now.
King Stannis is my king and the legitimate king by the laws of gods and man.
Long live the King in the North!
Long live the King in the North!
I would love to see Kings Landing!
We ride with the king in the north, long live the king ...
We ride with the king in the north for the time being.
Long live the King in the North!
We ride with the king in the north for the time being.
We sail with the king of salt and rock.
We sail along side in the Iron fleet along side the Greyjoys.
House Coldwater is sworn to the Warden of the East, Lysa Arryn, until Robin come of age.
House Waxley is sworn to the Warden of the East, Lysa Arryn, until Robin come of age.
We are sworn to the Warden of the West ...
Have you seen the Young Wolfe? Oh my, Im smitten.
We ride with House Tully for now. Stay away from those Blackwoods, they are a scourge on the Riverlands.
We ride with House Tully, the Lord Paramount of the Trident.
We ride with House Tully, the Lord Paramount of the Trident.
We are swore to King Renly, but my father is in the riverlands leading the Brotherhood without Banners, I hear.
I swore vows to the Warden of the South.
I swore vows to the Warden of the South.
I will follow the House Tyrell into battle.
We serve at the pleasure of the Prince of Dorne.
House Jordayne swore vows to the prince of Dorne.
House Qorgyle swore vows to the prince of Dorne.
The High King of Sarnor bows before no man, but those dothraki savages surely humbled my ancestors.
I am the blood of the dragon, its time to claim what is rightfully mine.
I raised young griff like he was mine, now hes my king.
We sail along side in the Iron fleet along side the Greyjoys.
The Skagosi rule themselves, we know no king but the ones residing in our frozen halls.
We ride with House Tully, the Lord Paramount of the Trident, no matter the cost.
The Golden Company will forever back Young Griff as he claims his birthright.
Well done, {?PLAYER.GENDER}madam{?}sir{\?}. Keep the money and wine coming our way, and theres no foe in Westeros or Essos you need fear.[ib:convo_approving]
You will not be dissapointed {?PLAYER.GENDER}madam{?}sir{\?}. You will not find better warriors in all Westeros or even Essos.[ib:convo_approving]
